SUMMARY:CSI: Crime Scene Idiots
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:A murder has been committed. The clues are everywhere. Two clow
 ns enter the scene and ask “What happened?” CSI: Crime Scene idiots ble
 nds improv and clowning with trope-heavy\, crime-drama parody. Guided by th
 e audience\, an investigation unfolds\, complete with mishandling of forens
 ic evidence\, dramatic smoke breaks and the hot pursuit of a fleeing suspec
 t. Join incompetent detectives Will Power and Dana Might for a new case eve
 ry night. Where you will become the key witness in a murder investigation! 
 With optimism and courage\, but no credibility or expertise. Can they solve
  the crime in 45 minutes and catch a killer? Expect to be surprised\, to be
  suspected and to laugh in the face of due process. Created and performed b
 y comedic duo Mabel Rack and James Allen. Directed by Hay-lin Cai.\nMore in
 fo: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/csi-crime-scene-idiots/
